profile:
Pratt Homes is Barrie's largest builder since 1890. They have been building condominiums, townhomes and detached home communities in the Barrie area for 124 years.  Pratt Homes is the founder of the successful CMHC approved Rent to Own program and has various sweat equity and low deposit structure programs helping homeowners afford their dream of home ownership.  Pratt Homes has a perfect Tarion New Home Warranty ranking and is considered one of the most professional and experienced builders in Ontario.  Pratt Homes has been awarded several Tarion, SAM and ACE, Chamber and HUDAC awards for homebuilding.

www.pratthomes.ca
